wt.facade.persistedcollection

Class PersistedCollectionEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • wt.events.KeyedEvent
      • wt.facade.persistedcollection.PersistedCollectionEvent

  • public final class PersistedCollectionEvent
extends KeyedEvent
    Used to represent events occurring within the PersistedCollection services. This event supports multiple object event targets. For most operations, the event target will either be a WTCollection of PersistedCollectionHolders or PersistedCollectables.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
